{"tid":2309848,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蛀牙，要杜牙根同做牙套，太貴冇錢做，所以要剝牙","createTime":"2020-12-03T00:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T12:54:00.000Z","uid":385014,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6534bf68a265d60096a3bd2a1b9a483ba5149c92","tid":2309848,"uid":385014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T00:19:35.000Z","msg":"一邊剝牙，一邊淚流滿臉，牙醫問我是否非常害怕剝牙，我草草敷衍說是。<br />\n<br />\n我心痛的不是剝牙的痛，而是因為自己經濟能力不許可，負擔不起修補牙齒，只能用上數百元剝掉牙齒。為正在失去一顆「受之父母」的牙齒而感到非常無力及心痛，所以悲從中來。<br />\n<br />\n最近太太懷孕了，我太太跟我說生小朋友一定十分痛，你連剝牙也淚流滿臉，生小朋友的痛你一定承擔不了。<br />\n<br />\n我聽了這一句話之後在床上暗暗流淚了一整晚。<br />\n我是有愧受之父母感到悲傷而落涙；另一個則是迎接新生命來臨歡樂的落涙。<br />\n<br />\n兩者的落涙雖然不能作對比，但是卻令我有愧受之父母之心更沉重。<br />\n<br />\n身體髮膚，受之父母，不敢毀傷，孝之始也；<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da2ef32afb870f144204cd5779cb31e48bf69c4","tid":2309848,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T00:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f002e866d219a0aa905d0488bfabf51b868ea974","tid":2309848,"uid":87820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T00:56:21.000Z","msg":"蛀牙冇錢整牙套仲生小朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34f8977d67fba326f5aa84c594e8337e6346d04","tid":2309848,"uid":385014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f002e866d219a0aa905d0488bfabf51b868ea974","tid":2309848,"uid":87820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T00:56:21.000Z","msg":"蛀牙冇錢整牙套仲生小朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=